  "instructions": [
    "Rinse 1 cup lentils under cold water until clear.",
    "In a kazan cauldron, heat 2 tbsp olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add diced carrot, sliced celery, and fennel to the cauldron, sauté for 5 minutes until slightly softened.",
    "Stir in 1 tsp cumin and 1 bay leaf, cooking for 1 minute to release aromas.",
    "Add the rinsed lentils and 4 cups boiling water, bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 30 minutes, stirring occasionally, until lentils are tender but still chewy.",
    "Stir in 1 tbsp aji amarillo paste, 1 tbsp aji panca paste, and 1 tsp salt, cooking for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Finish with freshly ground pepper, chopped cilantro, and serve hot."
  ],
